{'text': 'It provides a very beautiful view of the entire city. You can see the Stunning Panoramic Views  from (200m) 57 stories high.

You have two options for tickets, non-peak hours before 4 pm or peak hours ticket after 4:30 pm. We visited the observation deck on Marina Bay in the afternoon. It was non - peak hours.

Last entry to SkyPark Observation Deck for non - peak hour is at 4:00pm and peak hour is at 8:30 pm. They  recommend spending 45 minutes - 1 hour at the SkyPark Observation Deck. There is a roof top bar. So you can relax at the observation deck with a drink.', 'languageCode': 'en'}

